(49, 'Our Admin', 'Our Admin', 'Our Admin', 'Our Admin', 'Our Admin', 'Our Admin', '', '', '92', 'Dynamic Tools Pvt. Ltd', '<div align="justify"><font size="2"><strong>Dynamic Tools Pvt. Ltd</strong> is a Highly supportive place to work. The Admin Department of Dynamic Tools Pvt. Ltd enjoys the work of facilitating company chores going smooth.We believe that our strength and ability to succeed lies in our people. At Dynamic Tools Pvt. Ltd, freedom inspires ideas and the working environment nurtures excellence. The knowledge of one becomes the knowledge of all, shared on a common platform. What we offer to our employees is an accelerated career path and a host of other tangible and intangible benefits.<br />\r\n</font> <font size="2"><br />\r\nThe admin work force looks after the Accounts, Finance and all other company related Administrative chores wisely. The experience at Dynamic Tools Pvt. Lt, gives our employees an enriched memories of the whole life. We make continuous efforts to provide a sense of community, security and mutual trust. We treat our employees with warmth, dignity and respect.<br />\r\n</font> <font size="2"><br />\r\n</font> <font size="2"><strong>Our Admin:</strong><br />\r\n</font> <font size="2"><br />\r\nHaving acquired utmost professionals as Personnel in our Industry, the quality of Service and Product output and response towards our client is Highly Professional. Our employees never compromise in the quality of work they deliver both to the clients and to the office administration. Dynamic Tools Pvt. Ltd has loads of Wonderful memories from Clients expressing their Satisfaction level and pleasantness to make longterm associations with us.</font></div>', '2013-05-07'),
(50, 'About us', 'About us', 'About us', 'About us', 'About us', 'About us', '', '', '8047', 'About us', '<div align="justify">\r\n<p>&ldquo; Development is never an accident &rdquo;,<br />\r\nIt is always the result of high intension, sincere efforts, intelligent direction and skillful execution; it represents the wide choice of many alternatives&rdquo;.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>G.R.SURYA RAJ, M.D.</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nDYNAMIC TOOLS PVT LTD is a leading Manufacturer and Exporter of Medium Range Cigarette Machinery and Critical Spare parts for high-speed Cigarette Machinery. Our machinery Equipment combines superior design with Customized service for various multinational and local customers.<br />\r\nMr.G.R.Surya Raj, promoter of<strong> DYNAMIC TOOLS PVT.LTD</strong>., a Technocrat, worked for HMT, Hyderabad for over 15 years.&nbsp; During the period of working with HMT, he gained knowledge of highly sophisticated machine tool manufacturing machines on CNC, HMC and many state-of-the art machines.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn 1996 he had established <strong>DYNAMIC TOOLS PVT.LTD</strong>., with an objective to start manufacturing&nbsp; critical spares and spare assembly for reputed cigarette manufacturing companies like ITC Group of Companies&nbsp; and many more domestic cigarette giants who were importing those items from their machinery suppliers.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; In a short period, through consistent efforts the company has become familiar with renowned cigarette-manufacturing companies with its promising leaps.&nbsp; <br />\r\nSince 2002 onwards the <strong>DYNAMIC TOOLS PVT LTD</strong> unit acquired sophisticated machinery items, developed vendors ,with its well-experienced technical experts and skilled labor, started to manufacture Medium Speed Cigarette Machines called as DYNAMICS 2500 with a combination of Filter Assembler. Since then, our expertise and productivity has paved path for many more innovative technological evolutions.<br />\r\nMr.G.R.Surya Raj boundless exposure to international trends and developments has proven fruitful for producing internationally standardized machinery. In 2006 Dynamic Tools has participated in international fairs like <strong>Bali International Tobacco Fair held at Bali, Indonesia,</strong> in April 2007 World Tobacco Middle East Dubai Fair held at Dubai and&nbsp; also participated in <strong>Tabexpo 2008 Fair </strong>held at Paris.<br />\r\nAlso the Company has expanded its global horizons by our experts visiting leading cigarette machinery manufactures at U.K, Germany, Dubai, Malaysia and other places. Consequently, developed truly professional rapport with our international clients and secured orders for supply of spares, sub assembly sets and also machinery items gradually.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn 2009 the company has developed a DYNMICS - 250 Shell &amp; Slide Packer which produces 250 packets per minute.<br />\r\nThe latest development from DYNAMIC TOOLS is <strong>Dynamics HLP-180 </strong>which is going to be launched in August 2010 into the market.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Today, the continuous efforts and motivate mind to release a perfection in quality made DYNAMIC TOOLS Pvt.Ltd., in to a new heights with a 24000 Sft of Shop floor equipped with sophisticated machinery and 150 skilled man power with an enthusiastic quality service back up.</strong></p>\r\n</div>', '2013-05-07'),
